## ⚠️ Tailwind v4 Critical Rules

### NO tailwind.config.js
Tailwind v4 does NOT use `tailwind.config.js`. Configuration lives in CSS:

```css
/* src/styles/tailwind.css */
@import 'tailwindcss';
@plugin '@tailwindcss/forms';

@theme {
  --color-brand-primary: oklch(0.55 0.22 250); /* customize per site */
  --font-sans: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui;
}
```

```tsx
// ❌ WRONG — tailwind.config.js does not exist in this project
// ✅ CORRECT — edit src/styles/tailwind.css @theme block
```

### PostCSS Plugin
```js
// postcss.config.js — DO NOT CHANGE
module.exports = {
  plugins: {
    '@tailwindcss/postcss': {},
  },
}
```

