## Class Merging with clsx

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT — use clsx for conditional classes
import clsx from 'clsx'

function Button({ variant = 'solid', color = 'slate', className, ...props }) {
  return (
    <button
      className={clsx(
        'inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full py-2 px-4 text-sm font-semibold',
        variant === 'solid' && color === 'blue' && 'bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-500',
        variant === 'outline' && 'border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50',
        className
      )}
      {...props}
    />
  )
}
```

